{"article_id":"NWIIS3rl0oEKf7OC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump compared the impeachment inquiry against him to `` a lynching '' on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"drawing condemnation","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"for comparing a congressional process to vigilante murders","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"aimed mostly at black Americans .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"`` All Republicans must remember","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"what they are witnessing here - a lynching .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"But we will WIN ! ''","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` What the hell is wrong with you ? ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"tweeted Rep. Bobby Rush , D-Ill.","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"`` Do you know","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"how many people","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who look like me","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"have been lynched , since the inception of this country , by people","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"who look like you .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"Delete this tweet . ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Rep. Karen Bass , D-Calif. , chair of the Congressional Black Caucus , said","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Trump `` is once again using racial rhetoric","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to distract from the truth -","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"his corrupted behavior is weakening the integrity of our democracy . ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Bass added","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that the president `` is comparing a constitutional process to the prevalent and systematic brutal torture and murder of thousands ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"I repeat ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"thousands of African Americans in this country .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"It 's unacceptable . ''","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"who lost to Trump in the 2016 GOP primaries ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"tweeted","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that the president is not `` a victim ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"and that `` to equate his plight to lynching is grotesque . ''","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"White House spokesman Hogan Gidley denied","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that Trump considers himself a lynching victim ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` he 's not comparing himself to those dark times . ''","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Instead ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Gidley said ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"the president was criticizing his treatment by Democrats and journalists","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"whom","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"he said","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"have called for his impeachment","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"ever since he was elected","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"Gidley also said","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Trump has accomplished many things for African-Americans ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"citing low unemployment rates and a criminal justice reform bill .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Trump has attacked House Democrats ' impeachment investigation as political .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"But Tuesday was the first time","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"he used the term `` lynching . ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"In general , a lynching is the hanging of an accused person","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"without benefit of a trial","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"- a fate","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"often visited on black Americans in the pre-civil rights era .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"The NAACP reports","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that from 1882 to 1968 , there were 4,743 lynchings in the United States ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and of these , 3,446 were black .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"In the decades after the Civil War and Reconstruction ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"the NAACP history said ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` lynchings were becoming a popular way","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"of resolving some of the anger","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that whites had in relation to the free blacks . ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Impeachment inquiry :","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Diplomat","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"who called Trump Ukraine policy 'crazy '","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to testify in impeachment probe","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Rep. Jim Clyburn , D-S.C. ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"who had the tweet read to him during an interview on CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"said :","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"`` That is one word","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"no president ought to apply to himself .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"You know ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"I 've studied presidential history quite a bit ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and I do n't know","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"if we 've ever seen anything quite like this . ''","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"A few Republican lawmakers took Trump to task for his `` lynching '' comment .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Rep. Adam Kinzinger , R-Ill. , a frequent critic of Trump , tweeted","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"that `` we can all disagree on the process , ''","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"but terms like `` lynching '' should never be used .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"`` The painful scourge in our history has no comparison to politics ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"and @ realDonaldTrump should retract this immediately , ''","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Kinzinger said .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` May God help us to return to a better way . ''","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"House Republican leader Kevin McCarthy , R-Calif. , said","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"`` that ' s not the language","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"I would use , \"","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"though he defended Trump 's complaints about the Democrat-led impeachment efforts .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"\" It ' s very clear that what the Democrats are doing here does not have due process ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"is not fair in the process ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"is not something","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"this House has done ever in the past , ''","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"McCarthy said .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Another Republican , Sen. Lindsey Graham of South Carolina , defended the president 's word choice as `` pretty well accurate . ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"He told reporters","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that the impeachment investigation is a `` sham '' and a `` joke . '' `","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"` So yeah , ''","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Graham said ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"`` this is a lynching in every sense . ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Sen. Tim Scott , R-S.C. , Graham 's South Carolina colleague and the only African American Republican in Congress , questioned Trump 's language","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"if not his sentiment .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"`` There ' s no question","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"that the impeachment process is the closest thing to a political death row trial ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"so I get his absolute rejection of the process , ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Scott told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"`` I wouldn ' t use the word 'lynching . ' ''","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Historian Kevin Kruse wrote on Twitter","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that `` comparing impeachment proceedings to a lynching is even more insulting","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"when you 've cozied up to the very forces of white supremacy","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"that historically have used lynching as a tool","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"to terrorize racial minorities . ''","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"House Democrats are investigating Trump over a whistleblower complaint","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"that accused Trump of asking a foreign country","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"- Ukraine -","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"to investigate one of his domestic political opponents , former Vice President Joe Biden .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"As part of a series of familiar-looking tweets","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"decrying the investigation as political ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Trump also made a threat against future Democratic presidents .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"`` So some day ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"if a Democrat becomes President","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"and the Republicans win the House , even by a tiny margin ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"they can impeach the President ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"without due process or fairness or any legal rights , ''","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"The tweet came a day after Trump complained","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"that Republicans have not been aggressive enough","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"in defending him .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"`` Republicans have to get tougher and fight , ''","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"Trump said in a Cabinet meeting Monday .","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"`` We have some","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"that are great fighters ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"but they have to get tougher and fight","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"because the Democrats are trying to hurt the Republican Party for the","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"( 2020 )","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"election . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":263,"left":0,"right":262,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":238,"right":261,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":175,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":147,"right":174,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":135,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":1,"right":134,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":133,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","n